    "name": "Rosbeh",
    "profile": "Fusing a furious flurry of unconventional sounds to rich electronic soundscapes, Hamburg-based artist Rosbeh is an emerging artist currently making his mark on the global music scene. Inspired by artists like Bonobo, his style is eclectic and oozing with originality. He often combines piano lines with electronic beats. A highly versatile artist, he dips into a range of genres from downtempo and lofi techno, all the way to deep-house. He’s known for his electrifying performance style, with his timeless tracks serving as the perfect soundtrack for a booming club or even just a chilled night in.\r\n\r\nRosbeh first made his mark back in 2017 with his debut EP “The Journey In My Head”, a piano fuelled ambient floor-filler in which each song is connected to various events in his life that affected him. Two years later he put out his first electric dance track with acclaimed singer Hadja called “Feel”. He released the single independently and reached over 1 million streams on Spotify alone. Sinc",
